name: Explosive Power / Climb 5
description:
Just like attacking on a climb, this session requires you to produce a short, high power effort before settling into a 5-minute low cadence, threshold effort. Alternate between standing and sitting every minute during the 5min efforts. The session then finishes with a 10min, high cadence effort.
